summary: Remember when I said Eve and Villanelle would be on the run together and move into a cabin in Alaska and fuck all day? I...
body:
Remember when I said Eve and Villanelle would be on the run together and move into a cabin in Alaska and fuck all day? I realized my headcanon is getting more precise. I am by now convinced that they are going to steal a car because they obvsly have to get to their love cabin, so its gonna be one epic road trip - and Villanelle insists on taking a cool OLD car and later Eve realizes she was just looking for one with a cassette player because she has a fucking road trip mixtape full of sappy 80s songs that she wants to sing with her. She made that for Eve, just in case this would happen… and she brought a huge bag of snacks.

And they’ll make love in the backseat because Roxette tells them to in “Sleeping in my car”…

I think I have to write this. And make a matching spotify playlist.

blog.title: "Darling Eve, I hope you haven't forgotten about me..."
blog.description: "I think about you all the time... I think about what you're wearing and what you're doing and who you're doing it with. I think about what friends you have. I think about what you eat before you work and what shampoo you use and what happened in your family. I think about your eyes and your mouth and what you feel when you kill someone. I think about what you have for breakfast. I just want to know everything..."
